# Property `attributes`

The `attributes` property nested inside a [`link`](../json/property-link) object allows you to add custom attributes to be applied to the generated link. You must thus be aware that it might break the email lay-out or responsiveness in some clients.


```javascript
{
    "subject" : "link example",
    "from" : "info@example.com",
    "content" : {
        "blocks" : [ {
            "type" : "button",
            "label" : "Click me",
            "link" : {
                "url" : "http://www.dustsckr2000.com/models/P2000",
                "title": "Yes, you can click me",
                "attributes" : {
                    "data-test" : "Hello world"
                }
            }
        } ]
    }
}
```
